    {
      "note": "Summary of Original Version",
      "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 277 to define \"light engine\"; require a crew of at least 2 persons during operation of a train or light engine; amend KRS 277.990 to include penalties on railroad companies for crews of less than 2 persons."
